{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ecommerce-api-3-2-5",
    "name": "E-commerce API (Refactor 3.2.5)",
    "description": "Test flow E2E sau khi refactor module User + Category + Product + Variant + Image sang Lombok + MapStruct.\n\n## Cách dùng\n1. Setup MySQL chạy port 3309 + app chạy port 8080\n2. Chạy 2 request trong folder **0. Setup**: Register Admin → Register Seller\n3. **QUAN TRỌNG**: Vào MySQL chạy SQL update role (xem mô tả của request `Register Admin`)\n4. Chạy 2 request trong folder **1. Auth**: Login Admin → Login Seller (token auto lưu)\n5. Chạy các module theo thứ tự: Category → Product → Variant → Image\n6. Mỗi request `Create *` tự lưu id vào variable để request sau dùng\n\n## Variables auto-saved\n- `adminToken`, `sellerToken` (từ Login)\n- `categoryRootId`, `categoryChildId`, `categoryGrandchildId` (từ Create Category)\n- `productId` (từ Create Product)\n- `variantId` (từ Create Variant)\n- `imageId` (từ Upload Image)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "admin@test.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "Admin@123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sellerEmail", "value": "seller@test.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sellerPassword", "value": "Seller@123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sellerToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryRootId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryChildId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryGrandchildId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "variantId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "imageId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Setup (Register)",
      "description": "Tạo 2 user. SAU KHI tạo xong, BẮT BUỘC chạy SQL sau trong MySQL:\n\n```sql\nUSE ecommerce_db;\nUPDATE users SET role = 'ADMIN'  WHERE email = 'admin@test.com';\nUPDATE users SET role = 'SELLER' WHERE email = 'seller@test.com';\n```\n\nLý do: API register tạo user với role mặc định CUSTOMER. Project chưa có admin endpoint để promote role.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Admin candidate",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Admin Test\",\n  \"phone\": \"0900000001\",\n  \"address\": \"Hà Nội\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Seller candidate",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{sellerEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{sellerPassword}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Seller Test\",\n  \"phone\": \"0900000002\",\n  \"address\": \"TP.HCM\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "description": "Login 2 user → auto lưu accessToken vào collection variable.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Admin (auto save adminToken)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('✓ adminToken saved');",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('✗ accessToken not found in response');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
